c: 17
v: 78
t: "Ita Swalaah (minamato) kubva masikatikati kusvika parima reusiku (minamato yeDhuhr, Asr, Maghrib neIsha), uye verenga Qur’aan mangwanani-ngwanani (munamato wemangwanani, Fajr). Zvirokwazvo, kuverenga Qur’aan mangwanani zvinopupurwa (nengirozi dzemasikati nedzeusiku dzinotarisa vanhu)"